# Los Angeles Rust User Group

This is the website for members of the Rust Los Angeles user group. We normally meet once per month on a Wednesday evening. Please see our [meetup.com page](https://www.meetup.com/Rust-Los-Angeles/) for more details.

## Open Source

The user group has been working on some open source software written in Rust. You can check out our projects on [github](https://github.com/rust-los-angeles/).

## Contacts

Please get in touch with @hjr3 if you have any questions about Rust or this user group.
